'''Arsenicals''' are [[chemical compound]]s that contain [[arsenic]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Arsenicals - MeSH - NCBI |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/mesh/68001152}}</ref> In a military context, the term '''arsenical''' refer to toxic arsenic compounds that are used as [[chemical warfare agent]]s. This include [[blister agent]]s, [[blood agent]]s and [[vomiting agent]]s.<ref>{{cite book |title=Handbook of chemical and biological warfare agents |publisher=CRC Press |isbn=9780849314346 |edition=2nd}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Compendium of chemical warfare agents |publisher=Springer |isbn=9780387346267}}</ref>
